(5896, 25, 'Michael Ward', 'Englad Flag', '29 x 23 cm, Paint and Oil Pastel on Paper', 'I felt like doing the England flag, because I like the colours and I love our country. To show respect for the soldiers that go to war I felt that I should do a picture for them.', 'england-flag.jpg', NULL),
