(5872, 36, 'Ilona Santha', 'Year of the Horse', '41 x 28cm, Paint on paper', 'Ilona was part of an art group who were exploring the theme of Chinese New Year.  She worked with an adult to explore the textures and colours of paint and then used the tips of her fingers to paint onto the picture of the horse.', 'year-of-the-horse.jpg', NULL),
(5871, 36, 'Daniel Schofield', 'Aboriginal Hand Prints', '60 x 42cm, Paint & stone textures on paper', 'The learning outcomes for this project were to explore stone textures and to create an image using stencils and dots of colour to reflect traditional aboriginal art.', 'aboriginal-hand-prints-5.jpg', NULL),
