(5492, 33, 'Deryn Austin', 'The Eye of Inspiration', '41 x 29cm, Watercolour', 'We get inspiration through our eyes. You can tell what people are like and their emotions through their eyes.', 'the-eye-of-inspiration.jpg', NULL),
(5491, 33, 'Clementine Simon', 'Hidden Expression', '41 x 29cm, Watercolour, glitter', 'I painted with watercolour to give a delicate flowing image ant to portray gentleness and dignity.', 'hidden-expression.jpg', 2),
(5490, 33, 'Hollie Causton', 'Mardi Gras Girl', '19 x 26cm, Papier mache, paint, feathers, beads', 'I like the colours, shapes and patterns of the Mardi Gras masks in New Orleans', 'mardi-gras-girl.jpg', NULL),
(5489, 33, 'Jade Owens', 'Simply Regal', '18 x 22cm, Papier mache, paint', 'My mask was inspired by Mardi Gras. Gold for power, purple for justice and red represents the passion of the festival. I like the neatness of symmetry.', 'simply-regal.jpg', NULL),
(5488, 33, 'Daisy Scott', 'Majestic Identity', '20 x 23cm, Papier mache, paint, feathers', 'I chose the name because you put the mask on and it transforms you into a completely different person. I was inspired by Mardi Gras.', 'majestic-identity.jpg', NULL),
(5487, 33, 'Ciara Cuthbert', 'Autumn Glow', '23 x 29cm, Papier mache, wax crayon, nail varnish, leaves, twigs, paint', 'I have tried to capture autumn fading into winter, the leaves curled up before they rot. I want the leaves to contrast on the iridescent background.', 'autumn-glow.jpg', NULL),
(5486, 33, 'Amy Doolan', 'The Midnight Sky', '20 x 27cm, Papier mache, poster paint, feathers', 'My work was inspired by Mardi Gras and the night sky, how the stars shine and make shapes and patterns.', 'the-midnight-sky.jpg', NULL),
(5485, 33, 'Molly Hammond', 'The Midnight Mask', '26 x 12cm, Papier mache, poster paint, beads', 'My mask is based on Mardi Gras', 'the-midnight-mask.jpg', NULL),
(5484, 33, 'Emily Earley', 'Fabulous Festival', '32 x 22cm, Papier mache, poster paint, feathers, artificial flowers, beads', 'This is a Mardi Gras mask which signifies the passion of the festival, the fun and glamour.', 'fabulous-festival.jpg', NULL),
(5483, 33, 'Lauren Rice', 'Beads', '22 x 26cm, PPapier mache, poster paint, beads, feathers.', 'My mask was inspired by Mexican masks, the colours and textures.', 'beads.jpg', NULL),
(5482, 33, 'Daisy Hurst', 'Coffin Carrier', '42 x 58cm, Watercolour.', 'I read a lot of Gothic novels and watch films with a dark theme. This was inspired by the beauty found in the darker things in life.', 'coffin-carrier.jpg', NULL),
(5481, 33, 'Grace Beeley', 'Coffee and Cigarettes', '29 x 42cm, Pencil', 'This consists of a woman holding a coffee in one hand and a cigarette in the other. It was inspired by the film ?Breakfast at Tiffany?s? which stars Audrey Hepburn.', 'coffee-and-cigarettes.jpg', NULL),
(5480, 33, 'Rebecca O?Brien', 'Little Infinity', '59 x 42cm, Watercolour.', 'When I was younger, reading was my escape from a boring reality. I believe books can take you anywhere and I wanted to try and show that through my painting.', 'little-infinity.jpg', NULL),
(5479, 33, 'Thando Motaung', 'True Woman', '29 x 42cm, Watercolour, oil pastel.', 'I painted this to reflect my pride in my nationality.', 'true-woman.jpg', 3),
(5478, 33, 'Nisha Sharma', 'The Hand of Nature', '41 x 55cm, Watercolour, acrylic.', 'I was inspired by nature and culture. The lotus flower is a symbol of purity. The henna design represents the beauty of culture; the hand shows respect for nature by its gentle touch.', 'the-hand-of-nature.jpg', NULL),
