(8471, 86, 'John Louie Halog', 'The Twins', '30 x 21cm, Pencil Sketch', 'I was inspired by the work of Van Gogh and Picasso. I created this abstract pencil \r\nsketch based on gaming foes.', 'twins.jpg', NULL),
(8470, 86, 'Isis Tarbuck', 'Tasmanian Devil', '18 x 21cm, Pencil Sketch/ Chalk Pastels', 'I love drawing cartoons so I sketched my favourite character, the Tasmanian devil! \r\nThen I used chalk pastels to colour it in so that I could blend the colours.', 'tasmanian-devil.jpg', NULL),
(8469, 86, 'Alfie Davern', 'Bookshelf', '29 x 41cm, Chalk pastels on black card', 'I created this by blending chalk pastels to make it look like books on a shelf. I like \r\nthe dark background as it makes the colours stand out.', 'bookshelf.jpg', NULL),
(8468, 86, 'Sam Millington', 'The Eye of Illuminati', '22 x 20cm, Pencil Sketch/ Chalk Pastels', 'I am interested in the Illuminati and so I chose to complete my piece by creating this \r\nsymbol using chalk pastels. This is what people think it would look like, but really the \r\nsymbol is an owl in the middle standing on a perch with a circle of leaves surrounding it.', 'eye-of-illuminati.jpg', NULL),
(8467, 86, 'Daniel Croft', 'The War of The Dragons', '30 x 21cm, Pencil Sketch', 'My artwork depicts the battle between the elements of flame and sea. I am interested \r\nin mythical creatures, for example Minotaurs, so that is why I chose it for my artwork.', 'war-of-dragons.jpg', NULL),
(8466, 86, 'Abbey May Evans', 'Rainbow', '29 x 41cm, Chalk pastels', 'I looked at the work of Georgia O''Keeffe in art club and I loved her artwork. \r\nI created my own version using chalk pastels and smudging the colours together.', 'rainbow.jpg', NULL),
(8465, 86, 'Tiah Jones', 'Landscape', '29 x 41cm, Acrylic paint', 'I looked at the work of Vincent Van Gogh who painted on canvas using oil paints. \r\nHe inspires me and I love his paintings because they use vibrant colours. ', 'landscape.jpg', 1),
(8464, 86, 'Amber Connolly', 'Garden Girl', '30 x 21cm, Pencil sketch', 'I looked at the work of various sketch artists and loved the simple lines and shading \r\nthey used. I created my own design based on examples I had studied.', 'garden-girl.jpg', NULL),
(8463, 86, 'Neda Qasem', 'A touch of Autumn', '29 x 41cm, Acrylic paint', 'I was inspired by the work of Rene Magritte who created beautiful landscapes using \r\noil on canvas. I created my own version using acrylic paint and layering the colours \r\nto create the effect of autumn leaves. ', 'touch-of-autumn.jpg', 3),
(8462, 86, 'Shannon Gibbons', 'Flowers inspired by Georgia O''Keeffe', '44 x 29cm,Chalk pastels', 'I looked at the work of Georgia O''Keeffe in art club and I loved her artwork. \r\nI created my own version using chalk pastels and smudging the colours together.', 'georgia-okeefe-flowers.jpg', NULL),
(8461, 86, 'Seyram Danku', 'Keith Haring Tribute', '29 x 41cm, Acrylic paint', 'I created this piece based on some of Keith Harings artwork which I combined and \r\nrecreated to make my own unique design.', 'keith-haring-tribute.jpg', NULL),
