(8010, 97, 'Lucy Miller', 'Behind the Wall, Infinity', '36 x 46cm, Watercolour paint and pencil', 'The girl looks at the wall she built around her as it crumbles away, revealing some of the treasures and burdens of life that she has missed out on, in her plain grey world.', 'untitled-2.jpg', NULL),
